title: Photos: Extreme concentration, flashy shirts on display at Women's Bowling Association Tour Championship in Arlington
text: Danielle McEwan throws during the semi-finals of The Smithfield Professional Women's Bowling Association Tour Championship against Liz Johnson at the International Training and Research Center in Arlington, Sunday, September 13, 2015. McEwan would defeat Liz Johnson 278-224 and go on to defeat Stefanie Johnson 233-205 for the championship. (Brandon Wade/Special Contributor)
